<H3> <TI>   Correction to Item on MITI Factional `Wrangling' </TI></H3>
<F P=102>  WA1401145194 -- FOR OFFICIAL USE ONLY </F>
<F P=103> WA1401145194 </F>
<F P=104>  -- FOR OFFICIAL USE ONLY </F>



<TEXT>
Article Type:BFN 

  The following correction pertains to the item headlined 
"Factional `Wrangling' Within MITI Noted," published in the 12 
January East Asia DAILY REPORT Annex, pages 13-15: 
  Page 13, column two, first paragraph, first sentence, make 
read: ...a successor for Mr. Shigeru Sahashi (now deceased) who 
was.... (correcting name) 
  Page 14, column one, first paragraph, second sentence, make 
read: ...Mr. Kozo Watanabe, who is the deputy secretary general 
of Shinseito [Japan Renewal Party].... (correcting title) 

</TEXT>

