headline] 
  [Text] Pyongyang, January 14 (KCNA) -- The DPRK Government 
and people resolutely denounce the ever-more undisguised 
anti-DPRK, anti-socialist campaign of the Japanese reactionaries. 
  The Korean people will sharply watch the campaign with high 
