realise their ambition for overseas aggrandizement. 
  The DPRK and the United States have recently agreed to solve 
the problems for a fundamental solution of the nuclear issue on 
the Korean peninsula in a package deal at the third round of 
talks. So Japan is not requested to obtrusively make a fuss 
over the "nuclear issue" of the DPRK. 
  Japan must not take issue with the peaceloving DPRK but make 
a sincere apology and compensation to the Korean people for its 
past crimes and refrain from further acts obstructive to peace 
