President Kim Il-song in his New Year address. 
  "The policy of achieving the country's reunification through 
confederacy on the three principles of independence, peaceful 
reunification and great national unity, clarified once again by 
the great leader in his New Year address, fully conforms to the 
will and interests of the whole nation and serves as a highly 
