President Kim Il-song received telegrams from foreign party 
leaders on the new year. 
  The telegrams came from National Coordinator Oscar Ugarte 
Ubilluz of the Left Democratic Movement of Peru, General 
Secretary Luis Mateo Munos of the Socialist Party of Peru, 
Chairman Victor Sanchez Bilagra and General Secretary Ricardo 
Esli Garribia of the February Revolutionary Party of Paraguay, 
General Secretary Adelso Gonzalez Urdaneta of the People's 
Electoral Movement of Venezuela, President Angel Castro 
Lavarello of the National Executive Committee of the Left 
Revolutionary Union of Peru, Secretary General Ali Houdou of the 
Party of Revolution of Benin, National Chairman Emile Kibala Bey 
A Nsien of the Workers' Party of Zaire, National Chairman Otete 
Gaston Mboyo of the National Movement of the Genuine Lumumbist 
Combatants of Zaire, National Chairman Lambert Mende Omalanga of 
the Lumumba Congolese National Movement-Original of Zaire, 
Secretary General Mohamedoun Dicko of the Executive Committee of 
the African Party for the Solidarity and Justice of Mali, 
