Committee of the Sudanese Union-African Democratic Rally in 
Mali, and President Andriantiana Rakutuvau and General Secretary 
Gisele Rabesahala of the Party of the Congress for the 
Independence of Madagascar. 
  They extend warmest greetings to President Kim Il-song on 
the 
new year and wished him a long life in good health. 
  They wish the Korean people success in the building of 
socialism and the efforts for national reunification under the 
wise leadership of President Kim Il-song. 

</TEXT>

