Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] Seoul, Jan. 14 (YONHAP) -- The 21st Century 
Committee, created by South Korea and the United States, will 
hold its first meeting next month in Washington, the Foreign 
Ministry said Friday. 
  For three days, Feb. 17-19, prominent politicians, 
economists, scholars and businessmen, including U.S. Secretary 
