  [Text] Seoul, Jan. 14 (YONHAP) -- The Defense Security 
Command Friday questioned two former aides of Rep. Cho Sun-hwan 
of the United People's Party about a missing classified 
document, grilling them about how they had handled the material. 
  The two are former assistant Yi Un-chae, 38, and former 
