<H3> <TI>   KCNA Reports Appointment of New Forestry Minister </TI></H3>
<F P=102>  SK1401044294 Pyongyang KCNA in English 0433 GMT 14 Jan 94 </F>
<F P=103> SK1401044294 </F>
<F P=104>  Pyongyang KCNA </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> English </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] Pyongyang, January 14 (KCNA) -- The great leader 
Comrade Kim Il-song, president of the Democratic People's 
Republic of Korea, promulgated a decree of the Central People's 
Committee dated January 12 on the dismissal and appointment of 
the minister of forestry of the Administration Council. 
  According to the decree, Kim Chae-yul was relieved of his 
post and Yi Chun-sok was appointed to it. 

</TEXT>

