<DOCNO> FBIS3-47679 </DOCNO>
<HT>    "dreas011_a_94031" </HT>


<HEADER>
<AU>   FBIS-EAS-94-011 </AU>
Document Type:Daily Report 
<DATE1>  18 January 1994 </DATE1>

