Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] U.S. Senator John Kerry and his delegation arrived 
in Hanoi on Friday for a visit to Vietnam. 
  Working sessions were held immediately with Vietnamese 
Government officials. Speaking at a meeting with Deputy Foreign 
Minister Le Mai, Senator Kerry praised Vietnam's cooperation on 
